    "prohibited": "NEVER a target-list, an extraction recipe, or a by-industry-name 'mining is forbidden' verdict. Extraction is not banned as such; it is judged by measured harm to 子孫.",
    "routesTo": ["resilience", "de-monopolization", "restoration"]
  },
